OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778173555
OL,3,CSecond person dies after car crashes
OL,4,Cinto house in Lancashire
OL,6,FLancashire Police have revealed a
OL,7,Fsecond person has now died following a
OL,8,Fcar crash in Haslingden, Lancashire.
OL,10,FPolice say a VW Golf which had been
OL,11,Ftravelling on Helmshore Road left the
OL,12,Fcarriageway and struck the side of a
OL,13,Fhouse and then a retaining wall on
OL,14,FMonday night (May 4th).
OL,16,FThe driver of the Golf, a man in his
OL,17,F20s, died in hospital on Tuesday
OL,18,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
