PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778173555
OL,3,CSecond person dies after car crashes
OL,4,Cinto house in Lancashire
OL,6,FTwo young females, who were passengers
OL,7,Fin the car, both suffered severe
OL,8,Finjuries and were taken to hospital.
OL,10,FOne of them, aged 18, died in hospital
OL,11,Fon Tuesday night.
OL,13,FLancashire Police said:
OL,15,F"Our thoughts are very much with her
OL,16,Ffamily and loved ones at this sad and
OL,17,Fdistressing time. They are being
OL,18,Fsupported by specially trained family
OL,19,Fliaison officers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
