CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778173555
OL,3,CSecond person dies after car crashes
OL,4,Cinto house in Lancashire
OL,6,F"The other teenager remains in
OL,7,Fhospital in a serious condition.
OL,9,F"As officers investigate the cause of
OL,10,Fthe collision, we are continuing to
OL,11,Fappeal for witnesses, footage and
OL,12,Finformation.
OL,14,F"If you saw the collision or were in
OL,15,Fthe area at the time it happened and
OL,16,Fhaven't yet spoken to us, please get
OL,17,Fin touch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
