OL,3,CSecond person dies after car crashes
OL,4,Cinto house in Lancashire
OL,6,F"Anyone with dashcam/CCTV or Doorbell
OL,7,Ffootage from the area, again please
OL,8,Fcontact out officers.Call 101, quoting
OL,9,Flog 1623 of 4th May, or email our
OL,10,FSerious Collision Investigation Unit
OL,11,Fat SCIU@lancashire.police.uk."
